3
00:00:26,985 --> 00:00:28,319
<i>namaku Brooks Rattigan,</i>

4
00:00:28,403 --> 00:00:30,447
<i>tapi aku tak ingin hanya kau yang tahu,</i>

5
00:00:30,572 --> 00:00:32,907
<i>aku ingin seluruh dunia tahu,</i>

6
00:00:32,991 --> 00:00:34,826
<i>karena aku ingin mengubah dunia.</i>

7
00:00:37,579 --> 00:00:38,580
