196
00:09:44,667 --> 00:09:46,669
tapi aku bisa buka pintu sendiri.

197
00:09:47,420 --> 00:09:48,421
Terima kasih.

198
00:10:02,685 --> 00:10:03,853
Mau kuputarkan musik?

199
00:10:06,480 --> 00:10:08,816
Wow, kau menyediakan layanan yang bagus.

200
00:10:09,400 --> 00:10:11,944
Jangan bilang kau punya permen Mentos

201
00:10:12,028 --> 00:10:14,363
dan botol air kecil di kotak barangmu.

202
00:10:14,864 --> 00:10:15,781
Astaga, benar.

203
00:10:16,407 --> 00:10:18,659
Memenuhi fantasiku soal kencan
dengan sopir taksi.

204
00:10:20,244 --> 00:10:22,663
<i>Dalam 150 meter, belok kiri.</i>

205
00:10:22,747 --> 00:10:24,457
Tidak, kau akan terus jalan lurus.

206
00:10:24,540 --> 00:10:27,752
- Navigasi bilang...
- Jangan dengarkan robot, dengarkan aku.

207
00:10:27,835 --> 00:10:30,713
<i>Hitung ulang, dalam 60 meter, belok kanan.</i>

208
00:10:30,796 --> 00:10:32,381
Kau akan belok kiri di sini.

209
00:10:33,090 --> 00:10:34,216
Sekarang menepilah…

210
00:10:36,052 --> 00:10:37,470
dan kita sampai di sini.

211
00:10:37,845 --> 00:10:39,597
Ini bukan sekolahmu.
